<h2><font color="#0000ff">Draft Agenda</font></h2>
<BR>
<p>Participants are encouraged to take advantage of
a <b>poster session</b> to present recent results. 
The poster format allows people 
to have extended discussion regarding results of interest.  
Those who are 
presenting posters will have an opportunity to introduce 
their material briefly (one minute, one transparency) so 
the audience will know what is available.  There is limited 
space for posters; thus, please confirm whether you will 
give a poster so that we can reserve a space for you.</p>
<p>Please email <a href="mailto:pircs@iastate.edu">pircs@iastate.edu</a>
if you have questions about the agenda, or additional agenda items
to suggest.</p>
